CHANGELOG
=========

v0.0.3 (2024-09-03):
	Fixes:

	* Text following an "@" symbol that doesn't contain an "@" symbol will not
	  be filtered as a mention.

v0.0.2 (2024-08-14):
	Fixes:

	* Mentions can now appear at the start of a line.

v0.0.1 (2024-07-27):
	First public release.

 vim:tw=80:comments=:fo+=n:formatlistpat=^\\s*\\*\\s*
